        <mxCell id="FLXTgydPradgtQ5n2XYN-73" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EFF4FC;strokeColor=#8FC0FF;glass=0;align=left;fontSize=12;fontColor=default;fontFamily=Lato,proxima-nova,Helvetica Neue,Arial,sans-serif;verticalAlign=middle;shadow=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 130%;&quot;&gt;Conclude the experiment/survey. Optionally give the user a completion code or redirect them to an external URL. Always the last page in the list.&amp;nbsp;&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 4px;&quot;&gt;Path&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(77, 77, 77), rgb(171, 171, 171));&quot;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lucida Console&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;end&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
